[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "洞窟はやっぱ寒いね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_037_00831",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "そうそう。冷えるからお腹出さないほうがいいよ？\n私が言えた義理じゃないけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00832",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "聖地だから、九偉人の光る像とかあるかなーって\n思ったのに……もっと奥行ったらあるかな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_037_00833",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "慎重に進もう。九偉人の聖地といわれる洞窟、\n侵入者除けの罠があったりする可能性も……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_209_037_00834",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ああ、それは大丈夫。\nそれこそ、聖地だから、ね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00835",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "聖地だから……そっか、聖地なら多くの人が\n参拝に来るから、罠を仕掛けたら危ないもんね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00836",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "そうよ。それにここが聖地なら、信仰のために\nむしろしっかり整備されているはずだと思うわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00837",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "確かに。今は寂れて見えるけど、\n昔は整備されていたと思える跡がちょこっと見えるね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00838",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "あの～、今さらなんだけど、あなたは……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_037_00839",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "私はクレオ・ランターナ。ランターナ王女だよ。\nそして、特殊部隊「光星隊」の隊長なり！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00840",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "光星隊再結成の時まで、私も旅に参加するの。\nみんなと一緒にいたら、もっと強くなれる気がするから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00841",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "改めて、よろしくね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00842",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "よろしくお願いします……\nリアスが失礼をしないよう、しっかり見ていないと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_209_037_00843",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "もう！　しないってば！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_037_00844",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "聖地……洞窟、ひと気のない場所……\nお、いいのできたかも！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00845",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "冷たく、暗い私の心、吹き込んでくるのは\n温かなあの人の温もり……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00846",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "え？　なに急に？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_037_00847",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "お母さん、詩を作るのが好きなの。\n昔から変わってないんだね、その趣味",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00848",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "へえ、ポエム……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00849",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "誰も踏み入れたことのない私の聖地に、\nあなたの気配が忍び寄る……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00850",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "魔物",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ハッハッハッ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_732_037_00851",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "それは荒く、獣のような息遣い……\nって、魔物じゃないの！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00852",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "私の恋愛詩をなんかいやらしくしないでよね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00853",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "ひゃー、豪快……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_037_00854",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "繊細な詩とは正反対だな……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_209_037_00855",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "強くて詩も作れる……文武両道で素敵！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00856",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "あら、ほめてくれてありがと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00857",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "元々恋愛詩を書くのが趣味だったんだけど、\nどっちかというと向いてるのは荒事だったみたいでね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00858",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "吟遊詩人みたいなことをしたかったけど、\nいつの間にやらすっかり冒険者",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00859",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "まあでも、そのうち冒険自体楽しめるようになったし\n冒険譚とか詩の引き出しも増えたからよし！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00860",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "戦って歌える吟遊冒険者、なんて結構私に\n似合ってる気がするんだけど、どうかな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00861",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "すごく似合ってる！　素敵！\n私もそんな素敵な人になりたいよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00862",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ふふっ、今のクレオちゃんも十分素敵だけどね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00863",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "洞窟の出発前でも思ったけど\nレスナちゃんのお母さん、元気で、とっても若いよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_037_00864",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ふふ、私が小さい頃からずっとあんな感じなんだ。\n誰とでもすぐ仲良くなれちゃう、自慢のお母さん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00865",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]